---
title: Creole-inspired Prawn Rigatoni with cheese and a hint of lemon
description: This creamy Cajun pasta is a delight for the eyes and the tastebuds too. Featuring  Cajun-inspired spices enhanced with a dash of lemon juice and a crispy crumb topping. This is more than just your average pasta dish!
